# OptiScaler Client per-machine state. Never stow this: games.json holds the
# full Steam library with $HOME paths, Cache/ is ~200MB of re-downloadable DLLs,
# and config.json mixes prefs with volatile window geometry/timestamps. See
# fedora/bin/README.md (optiscaler-client). Defensive ignore so a stray
# `git add` of a stow tree can't leak it.
